<h2>The Taxonomy List</h2>
<p>This page shows you the taxonomies defined for your site, and the content types that they are associated with.
To edit a taxonomy, click on it's name. To create a new taxonomy, click on "Add a Taxonomy". For more information
on taxonomies and how to use them, see <a href="page?src=taxonomy&page=index">Taxonomies &amp; Bindings</a></p>